snippet.title: INVECTOR feat. Avicii (PS4 trailer)
snippet.description:
INVECTOR feat. Avicii

Visit: http://invectorgame.com

Turn up the volume and take rhythm gaming to new heights.

Fly solo or party with friends in a split screen race, as you join space pilot Stella on her journey from one stunning world to the next. 

Each hit song you play offers on the note level design and three difficulties to master.

In an exclusive collaboration, INVECTOR features superstar AVICII, experienced like never before.
